    {
      "title": "\\begin{array}{|c|c|c|c|}\\hline \\text{Montgomery ladder. Input: ladder state } (X_{QP}, X_{RP}, M, Y_P) \\\\ \\hline \\\\ 1 & \\bar{Y}_R = Y_P + 2 \\cdot M \\cdot X_{RP} & 8 & Y_P' = Y_P \\cdot F \\cdot G \\\\ 2 & E = X_{QP} - X_{RP} & 9 & K = H + M' \\\\ 3 & F = \\bar{Y}_R \\cdot E & 10 & L = K + M' \\\\ 4 & G = E^2 & 11 & M'' = X_{RP}' - K \\\\ 5 & X_{RP}' = X_{RP} \\cdot G & 12 & X_{SP} = H \\cdot L \\\\ 6 & H = \\bar{Y}_R^2 & 13 & X_{TP} = X_{RP}'^2 + Y_P' \\\\ 7 & M' = M \\cdot F & 14 & Y_P'' = Y_P' \\cdot H \\\\ \\hline \\end{array}",
